              "message": "D1 says AC fulfillment is proven by `metadata.json` task `done` plus `commit_hash`, but the current Phase 0-3 workflow makes `metadata.json` schema v5 identity-only and stores tasks/commit hashes in `impl-plan.json`. This points the migration at the wrong source of truth for task completion.",
